skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: clever real estate
des: Clever will help you find a top real estate agent and save thousands on commission. We do that by helping you List and sell your home for a flat fee of $3,000, or 1% if the home is more than $350,000 with a top-rated, full-service real estate agent. You don't pay anything until you close. We use Top local agents in every US city. And we're going to provide you with a Free consultation in 24 hours. To get started say, Alexa open Clever Real Estate
